WEBVTT

00:01:58.480 --> 00:02:01.480
She already knew
what I was just beginning to name.

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:06.376
That love is more than a rush of feeling

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:08.320
that happens to us if we're lucky.

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:12.480
Love is sweet labor.

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:14.656
Fierce.

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:16.216
Bloody.

00:02:16.240 --> 00:02:17.440
Imperfect.

00:02:18.160 --> 00:02:19.360
Life-giving.

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:22.960
A choice we make over and over again.

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:29.936
I am an American civil rights activist

00:02:29.960 --> 00:02:33.856
who has labored with communities
of color since September 11,